<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٦٣٨ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1810">خَلَفُ بْنُ خَالِدٍ الْقُرَشِيُّ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/985">بَكْرُ بْنُ مُضَرَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1149">جَعْفَرِ بْنِ رَبِيعَةَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4349">عِرَاكِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4184">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ مَسْعُودٍ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّ الْقَمَرَ انْشَقَّ فِي زَمَانِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>